Citigroup Said to Agree to Buy 9.9% Stake in Vietnam’s Horizon Securities

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-07-01T01:57:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/citigroup-said-to-agree-to-buy-9-9-stake-in-vietnam-s-horizon-securities.html
Citigroup Inc. (C)  is buying a stake
in  Vietnam ’s Horizon Securities Corp., according to two
people with knowledge of the matter.  The  U.S. bank  agreed to acquire 9.9 percent of closely
held Horizon for an undisclosed amount yesterday, the two
people said, declining to be identified before a public
announcement.  The transaction was reported earlier today by the Wall
Street Journal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
